ge test for `org.mortbay.util.TypeUtil`.\n\nAdded:\n\n- `tests/src/org.mortbay.jetty/jetty-util/6.1.26/src/test/java/org_mortbay_jetty/jetty_util/TypeUtilTest.java`\n\nThe new tests exercise:\n\n- `TypeUtil` static initialization, reaching the `Class#getMethod(...)` call sites.\n- Name/class mappings via `fromName` and `toName`.\n- `valueOf(...)` paths using registered primitive/wrapper `valueOf(String)` methods, reaching `Method#invoke(...)`.\n- Character and String handling.\n- String-constructor fallback using a public helper type, reaching `Class#getConstructor(...)` and `Constructor#newInstance(...)`.\n\nPer instruction, I did not run tests locally.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_05e80ae20a23ca3d0169f7810d780081a2a3f2e15baffe6f68\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1667, "output": 685, "cacheRead": 13312, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 15664, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777828097755, "responseId": "resp_05e80ae20a23ca3d0169f78102186c81a2b2b5d23aaa7aee34"}, "toolResults": []}
